| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4585 — Recovery Inhibition (worldleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 98615c8c-5d9b-5cb6-b353-78ebcbe687ee"
